graph TB
    subgraph "Startup Sequence"
        Start[docker compose up]
        
        Start -->|1. Start| FalkorDB["falkordb<br/>healthcheck: redis-cli ping"]
        Start -->|1. Start| Qdrant["qdrant<br/>no healthcheck"]
        
        FalkorDB -->|2. Wait for healthy| FalkorHealthy{Health Check<br/>Passing?}
        FalkorHealthy -->|Yes| FlaskStart["flask-api<br/>depends_on: service_healthy"]
        FalkorHealthy -->|No, retry<br/>interval: 10s<br/>retries: 5| FalkorHealthy
        
        Qdrant -->|2. Service started| FlaskStart
        
        FlaskStart -->|3. Initialize| InitGraph["init_memory_graph()<br/>app.py"]
        InitGraph -->|Connect| FalkorDB
        
        FlaskStart -->|3. Initialize| InitQdrant["init_qdrant()<br/>app.py"]
        InitQdrant -->|Connect| Qdrant
        
        FlaskStart -->|3. Start workers| Workers["Background Workers<br/>enrichment, embedding,<br/>consolidation, sync"]
        
        FlaskStart -->|4. Bind socket| Ready["Flask API Ready<br/>Listening on :8001"]
    end
    
    subgraph "Health Check Configuration"
        HealthConfig["test: redis-cli ping<br/>interval: 10s<br/>timeout: 5s<br/>retries: 5"]
    end
    
    FalkorDB -.->|configured by| HealthConfig